We Are Looking for:Experienced C++ developers, mid and senior, to join our team.The Project:Our customer is a global supplier of technology and services for the industrial, consumer goods and automotive sectors.The project consists of implementing a multi-functional interface for an electric bike (eBike) that was launched on the market. Among the features of the gadget are: high quality design, large color display, ability to download and install new applications, security, automated system for updates check, communication with mobile devices, synchronization with the online, gps, navigation, offline maps.Responsibilities:• Write quality code• Collaborate in driving the product in an automation testing direction• Be involved in the communication with the client• Do code review• Optimize current product in order to shape it for its utmostRequired Competencies:Must have:• Working experience with C/C++• Strong OOP knowledgeNice to have:• Qt programming experience• Embedded Linux• Experience working in Agile Scrum / Kanban methodology• Git work experience• German skills• Bike ridingWe Value:• Respect• Reliability• Strive for Excellence 





			    $(document).ready(function() { 
			    var allVideos = $('.job-video-container object, .job-video-container embed, .job-video-container iframe'); 
			    var oldWidth = allVideos.width();
			    var oldHeight =  allVideos.height();
			    var aspectRatioOS = oldHeight/oldWidth; 
			    allVideos.removeAttr('height').removeAttr('width');
			    function resizeVideoOSJS(){
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%;');
				var widthInit = allVideos.width();
				var heightInit = widthInit * aspectRatioOS;
				allVideos.attr('style', 'max-width: 600px; width: 100%; min-height: 220px; height: '+ heightInit +'px;');
				//.attr('width',  widthInit).attr('height', allVideos.height())    
			    }
			    resizeVideoOSJS();
				    window.onresize = resizeVideoOSJS; 
			    });
